data.description: Nice large Pool Home in desirable Indian Trails, close to schools, churches, library and shopping. Interior is newly painted, new Microwave and designer cabinets in Kitchen. Large Master Suite with walk-in closet, Luxurious Master Bathroom with bidet and walk-in tile shower. Large swimming pool, newly screened,(4year warrantee). This home is perfect for entertaining, spacious living room leading out to Lanai and Swimming pool. Family Room adjacent to Kitchen and guest wing. Freshly landscaped adds to the calming serene atmosphere. Great Price for a Large four bedroom home in desirable Indian Trails
